590static void
591build_action(olist, todo)
592 opt_t *olist;
593 ipmon_doing_t *todo;
594{
595 ipmon_action_t *a;
596 opt_t *o;
597 int i;
598
599 a = (ipmon_action_t *)calloc(1, sizeof(*a));
600 if (a == NULL)
601 return;
602
603 while ((o = olist) != NULL) {
604 /*
605 * Check to see if the same comparator is being used more than
606 * once per matching statement.
607 */
608 for (i = 0; macflags[i][0]; i++)
609 if (macflags[i][0] == o->o_type)
610 break;
611 if (macflags[i][1] & a->ac_mflag) {
612 fprintf(stderr, "%s redfined on line %d\n",
613 ipmon_yykeytostr(o->o_type), ipmon_yylineNum);
614 if (o->o_str != NULL)
615 free(o->o_str);
616 olist = o->o_next;
617 free(o);
618 continue;
619 }
620
621 a->ac_mflag |= macflags[i][1];
622
623 switch (o->o_type)
624 {
625 case IPM_DIRECTION :
626 a->ac_direction = o->o_num;
627 break;
628 case IPM_DSTIP :
629 a->ac_dip = o->o_ip.s_addr;
630 a->ac_dmsk = htonl(0xffffffff << (32 - o->o_num));
631 break;
632 case IPM_DSTPORT :
633 a->ac_dport = htons(o->o_num);
634 break;
635 case IPM_INTERFACE :
636 a->ac_iface = o->o_str;
637 o->o_str = NULL;
638 break;
639 case IPM_GROUP :
640 if (o->o_str != NULL)
641 strncpy(a->ac_group, o->o_str, FR_GROUPLEN);
642 else
643 sprintf(a->ac_group, "%d", o->o_num);
644 break;
645 case IPM_LOGTAG :
646 a->ac_logtag = o->o_num;
647 break;
648 case IPM_NATTAG :
649 strncpy(a->ac_nattag, o->o_str, sizeof(a->ac_nattag));
650 break;
651 case IPM_PACKET :
652 a->ac_packet = o->o_num;
653 break;
654 case IPM_PROTOCOL :
655 a->ac_proto = o->o_num;
656 break;
657 case IPM_RULE :
658 a->ac_rule = o->o_num;
659 break;
660 case IPM_RESULT :
661 if (!strcasecmp(o->o_str, "pass"))
662 a->ac_result = IPMR_PASS;
663 else if (!strcasecmp(o->o_str, "block"))
664 a->ac_result = IPMR_BLOCK;
665 else if (!strcasecmp(o->o_str, "nomatch"))
666 a->ac_result = IPMR_NOMATCH;
667 else if (!strcasecmp(o->o_str, "log"))
668 a->ac_result = IPMR_LOG;
669 break;

672 break;
673 case IPM_SRCIP :

704int
705check_action(buf, log, opts, lvl)
706 const char *buf, *log;
707 int opts, lvl;
708{
709 ipmon_action_t *a;
710 struct timeval tv;
711 ipmon_doing_t *d;
712 ipmon_msg_t msg;
713 ipflog_t *ipf;
714 tcphdr_t *tcp;
715 iplog_t *ipl;
716 int matched;
717 u_long t1;
718 ip_t *ip;
719
720 matched = 0;
721 ipl = (iplog_t *)buf;
722 ipf = (ipflog_t *)(ipl +1);
723 ip = (ip_t *)(ipf + 1);
724 tcp = (tcphdr_t *)((char *)ip + (IP_HL(ip) << 2));
725
726 msg.imm_data = ipl;
727 msg.imm_dsize = ipl->ipl_dsize;
728 msg.imm_when = ipl->ipl_time.tv_sec;
729 msg.imm_msg = (char *)log;
730 msg.imm_msglen = strlen(log);
731 msg.imm_loglevel = lvl;
732
733 for (a = alist; a != NULL; a = a->ac_next) {
734 verbose(0, "== checking config rule\n");
735 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_DIRECTION) != 0) {
736 if (a->ac_direction == IPM_IN) {
737 if ((ipf->fl_flags & FR_INQUE) == 0) {
738 verbose(8, "-- direction not in\n");
739 continue;
740 }
741 } else if (a->ac_direction == IPM_OUT) {
742 if ((ipf->fl_flags & FR_OUTQUE) == 0) {
743 verbose(8, "-- direction not out\n");
744 continue;
745 }
746 }
747 }
748
749 if ((a->ac_type != 0) && (a->ac_type != ipl->ipl_magic)) {
750 verbose(8, "-- type mismatch\n");
751 continue;
752 }
753
754 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_EVERY) != 0) {
755 gettimeofday(&tv, NULL);
756 t1 = tv.tv_sec - a->ac_lastsec;
757 if (tv.tv_usec <= a->ac_lastusec)
758 t1--;
759 if (a->ac_second != 0) {
760 if (t1 < a->ac_second) {
761 verbose(8, "-- too soon\n");
762 continue;
763 }
764 a->ac_lastsec = tv.tv_sec;
765 a->ac_lastusec = tv.tv_usec;
766 }
767
768 if (a->ac_packet != 0) {
769 if (a->ac_pktcnt == 0)
770 a->ac_pktcnt++;
771 else if (a->ac_pktcnt == a->ac_packet) {
772 a->ac_pktcnt = 0;
773 verbose(8, "-- packet count\n");
774 continue;
775 } else {
776 a->ac_pktcnt++;
777 verbose(8, "-- packet count\n");
778 continue;
779 }
780 }
781 }
782
783 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_DSTIP) != 0) {
784 if ((ip->ip_dst.s_addr & a->ac_dmsk) != a->ac_dip) {
785 verbose(8, "-- dstip wrong\n");
786 continue;
787 }
788 }
789
790 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_DSTPORT) != 0) {
791 if (ip->ip_p != IPPROTO_UDP &&
792 ip->ip_p != IPPROTO_TCP) {
793 verbose(8, "-- not port protocol\n");
794 continue;
795 }
796 if (tcp->th_dport != a->ac_dport) {
797 verbose(8, "-- dport mismatch\n");
798 continue;
799 }
800 }
801
802 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_GROUP) != 0) {
803 if (strncmp(a->ac_group, ipf->fl_group,
804 FR_GROUPLEN) != 0) {
805 verbose(8, "-- group mismatch\n");
806 continue;
807 }
808 }
809
810 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_INTERFACE) != 0) {
811 if (strcmp(a->ac_iface, ipf->fl_ifname)) {
812 verbose(8, "-- ifname mismatch\n");
813 continue;
814 }
815 }
816
817 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_PROTOCOL) != 0) {
818 if (a->ac_proto != ip->ip_p) {
819 verbose(8, "-- protocol mismatch\n");
820 continue;
821 }
822 }
823
824 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_RESULT) != 0) {
825 if ((ipf->fl_flags & FF_LOGNOMATCH) != 0) {
826 if (a->ac_result != IPMR_NOMATCH) {
827 verbose(8, "-- ff-flags mismatch\n");
828 continue;
829 }
830 } else if (FR_ISPASS(ipf->fl_flags)) {
831 if (a->ac_result != IPMR_PASS) {
832 verbose(8, "-- pass mismatch\n");
833 continue;
834 }
835 } else if (FR_ISBLOCK(ipf->fl_flags)) {
836 if (a->ac_result != IPMR_BLOCK) {
837 verbose(8, "-- block mismatch\n");
838 continue;
839 }
840 } else { /* Log only */
841 if (a->ac_result != IPMR_LOG) {
842 verbose(8, "-- log mismatch\n");
843 continue;
844 }
845 }
846 }
847
848 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_RULE) != 0) {
849 if (a->ac_rule != ipf->fl_rule) {
850 verbose(8, "-- rule mismatch\n");
851 continue;
852 }
853 }
854
855 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_SRCIP) != 0) {
856 if ((ip->ip_src.s_addr & a->ac_smsk) != a->ac_sip) {
857 verbose(8, "-- srcip mismatch\n");
858 continue;
859 }
860 }
861
862 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_SRCPORT) != 0) {
863 if (ip->ip_p != IPPROTO_UDP &&
864 ip->ip_p != IPPROTO_TCP) {
865 verbose(8, "-- port protocol mismatch\n");
866 continue;
867 }
868 if (tcp->th_sport != a->ac_sport) {
869 verbose(8, "-- sport mismatch\n");
870 continue;
871 }
872 }
873
874 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_LOGTAG) != 0) {
875 if (a->ac_logtag != ipf->fl_logtag) {
876 verbose(8, "-- logtag %d != %d\n",
877 a->ac_logtag, ipf->fl_logtag);
878 continue;
879 }
880 }
881
882 if ((a->ac_mflag & IPMAC_NATTAG) != 0) {
883 if (strncmp(a->ac_nattag, ipf->fl_nattag.ipt_tag,
884 IPFTAG_LEN) != 0) {
885 verbose(8, "-- nattag mismatch\n");
886 continue;
887 }
888 }
889
890 matched = 1;
891 verbose(8, "++ matched\n");
892
893 /*
894 * It matched so now perform the saves
895 */
896 for (d = a->ac_doing; d != NULL; d = d->ipmd_next)
897 (*d->ipmd_store)(d->ipmd_token, &msg);
898 }
899
900 return matched;
901}
